{
    "text": "wpidentity package",
    "created": "Tue, 05 Sep 2023 16:21:17 GMT",
    "type": "outline",
    "description": "A package that implements OAuth identity and a simple verb set with wordpress.com for Node.js apps.",
    "subs": [
        {
            "text": "I've reached a milestone in my <a href=\"https://github.com/scripting/wpIdentity\">wpidentity project</a>. ",
            "created": "Tue, 05 Sep 2023 16:10:53 GMT",
            "flBulletedSubs": "true",
            "subs": [
                {
                    "text": "It's now a <a href=\"https://www.npmjs.com/package/wpidentity\">package</a>, so it can be included in other servers. ",
                    "created": "Tue, 05 Sep 2023 16:21:32 GMT",
                    "flInCalendar": true
                },
                {
                    "text": "There's also an <a href=\"https://github.com/scripting/wpIdentity/blob/main/client/api.js\">interface</a> for browser-based clients to call through the server to wordpress.com. ",
                    "created": "Tue, 05 Sep 2023 16:21:36 GMT",
                    "flInCalendar": true
                },
                {
                    "text": "I've got a couple of simple demo apps running. ",
                    "created": "Tue, 05 Sep 2023 16:21:41 GMT",
                    "flInCalendar": true
                },
                {
                    "text": "Thinking of hooking it up to \"Drummer\" and/or \"FeedLand\". ",
                    "created": "Tue, 05 Sep 2023 16:21:45 GMT",
                    "flInCalendar": true
                },
                {
                    "text": "It's a richer interface to WordPress content than <a href=\"https://codex.wordpress.org/XML-RPC_MetaWeblog_API\">I've had</a>. ",
                    "created": "Tue, 05 Sep 2023 16:21:49 GMT",
                    "flInCalendar": true
                },
                {
                    "text": "Apparently this is using the same API that their browser-based client, <a href=\"https://github.com/Automattic/wp-calypso\">Calypso</a>, uses. ",
                    "created": "Tue, 05 Sep 2023 16:21:54 GMT",
                    "flInCalendar": true
                }
            ],
            "flInCalendar": true
        },
        {
            "text": "I have some definite ideas, but it's time for a break from development, off to schmooze with old and new Berkmanites. I'm one of the old ones -- it's been <a href=\"http://scripting.com/2003/03.html\">20 years</a> since I showed up there in 2003, believe it or not. ",
            "created": "Tue, 05 Sep 2023 16:21:59 GMT",
            "flInCalendar": true
        }
    ],
    "flInCalendar": true
}